{"tid":1030654,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗歐聯乏力，本賽季6場只進1球","createTime":"2019-02-21T05:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T15:09:46.000Z","uid":20634,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8ab939cbf0276a2265d379002611050fa7ff05","tid":1030654,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img1.qunliao.info/fastdfs3/M00/11/E6/ChONolxt_iaAO8MAAALBFiPch3w832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.qunliao.info%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2F11%2FE6%2FChONolxt_iaAO8MAAALBFiPch3w832.jpg&h=fd5cea7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2月21日凌晨，祖雲達斯在歐聯八分之一決賽首回合比賽中作客0-2不敵馬體會，C朗在比賽中沒有取得進球。<br />\n<br />\n本賽季加盟祖雲達斯之後，葡萄牙巨星已代表球隊在歐聯中出場6次，共計上場時間479分鐘，只打進1球，拿到1張紅牌，輸掉了三場比賽。<br />\n<br />\n上賽季效力皇馬時，C羅在歐聯中出場13次，打進了15球，最終幫助球隊連續第三年贏得冠軍。"},{"pid":"135d43629e185bb2b226ced1cf73ff4b944a09ee","tid":1030654,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"王騎召喚"},{"pid":"0786554d4b3f62a726c1f581e950d2a1fd420d42","tid":1030654,"uid":77788,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbdd0e5973db2187887e8655aeb23a5fce2b9601","tid":1030654,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"分組賽入條毛咩<br />\n淘汰賽先show真實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719936f2370cbcdf5a305bec2afbd546040b3349","tid":1030654,"uid":58811,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"幫朗迷打定留言<br />\n1. 蛆個中場無蝗咁靚<br />\n2. 之前紅咗一場啊，打少一場唔計<br />\n3. 隊波未夾熟<br />\n4. 隊友太廢<br />\n5. 個場太濕滑<br />\n6. 留力下場<br />\n7. 無人交波/走位<br />\n8. 個個都mark著球玉，起到腳都好勁啦/12碼中龍只不過被人接實<br />\n9. 我朗而家擦助攻數/ 顧著回後組織<br />\n10. 小花有幾多個歐聯啊？有幾多個世界盃啊？有幾多美州盃？敢唔敢黎意假啊？"},{"pid":"b31be6a4e3e11867a0be88fd56373f6fb70869eb","tid":1030654,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-